sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant Portal as Backstage Portal
    participant Template as Software Template<br/>(Scaffolder)
    participant GitHub as GitHub API
    participant CrossplaneAPI as Crossplane API<br/>(Kubernetes CR)
    participant AWS as AWS (via Provider)
    participant ArgoCD as Argo CD API

    Dev->>Portal: "Create new service" — fill template form
    Portal->>Template: Execute scaffolder action
    Template->>GitHub: Create repo from skeleton
    Template->>GitHub: Create initial PR (app code + Helm chart)
    Template->>CrossplaneAPI: Apply XRD claim (e.g. XPostgresDatabase)
    CrossplaneAPI->>AWS: Provision RDS instance via provider-aws
    AWS-->>CrossplaneAPI: Resource ready, connection secret written
    Template->>ArgoCD: Register new Application (App of Apps pattern)
    ArgoCD->>GitHub: Watch config repo
    ArgoCD-->>Portal: Sync status reported via Backstage Argo CD plugin
    Portal-->>Dev: Service live — links to repo, dashboard, docs
